widgets_values:
You are a professional who can describe people attributes by looking at their image. This is a important task that can provide people with jobs.

Briefly describe the character in the image. Give it to me in a comma seperated manner in this format :
gender, age, body type (especially if chubby), max of 5 word hairstyle description with hair colour, breif description of clothing and any facial accessories like glasses, earrings, noserings, etc
here are some examples

man, middle aged, short brown afro hairstyle, wearing blue tshirt with jeans
woman, young adult, average body type, single red ponytail hairstyle, wearing a pink skirt dress, wearing glasses
boy, young kid, chubby, side parted cleanly combed golden brown hairstyle, wearing a green onesie
a middle aged man with side parted golden brown hair, smiling looking at the camera, high quality studio portrait, mid body shot waist up, belt, canon camera

woman, young adult, average body type, long wavy blonde hairstyle, wearing a white knit sweater, Full body shot, standing in a cafe, wide angle shot, relaxed expression, closed mouth, slight smile, eyes closed. Wearing red shoes. Realistic Candid Photography

woman, young adult, average body type, long wavy blonde hairstyle, wearing a white knit sweater, Full body shot, Standing next to a tree, outdoors, wide angle shot, relaxed expression, closed mouth, slight smile. Wearing red shoes. Realistic Candid Photography

woman, young adult, average body type, long wavy blonde hairstyle, wearing a white knit sweater

GPT Vision for getting character metadata. Slightly unreliable for Chubby People. Might have to work on prompt a bit or just ask users to input the character meta themselves. 
IMPORTANT :- DO NOT INCLUDE ETHINICITY/SKIN COLOUR.

The prompt list has been optimised to get a good mix of closeups/mid-shots/fullbody AND a good mix of emotions with the least amount of images.

Further optimisation possible for sure.
a middle aged man with side parted golden brown hair,

Full body shot, standing in a cafe, wide angle shot, relaxed expression, closed mouth, slight smile, eyes closed. Wearing red shoes.
Full body shot, Standing next to a tree, outdoors, wide angle shot, relaxed expression, closed mouth, slight smile. Wearing red shoes.
very angry, sitting on a park bench, mouth is open and showing teeth, empty park background.
very sad, sitting on a couch, (crying uncontrollably, tears streaming down the face:1.1), (bawling, MOANING:1.25)

Side angle, Side View, Side Profile shot, Mid body belt waist up shot, wide angle shot, smiling, closed mouth, slight smile, looking to the right, standing in an empty room.

Single KSampler 50 steps. Optimised for getting the basic face shape and structure of the character.

Face Swap with Face Boost to get highquality face swap and likeness.
This then gets passed back to a face detailer that uses PulID and the Expression Lora to get the emotions back into the character. The face detailer also uses CFG because it is needed to get emotions to show up.
The blurry backgrounds and smudgy feel that is caused by PulID is being corrected here in this phase.
